<p>This invitation will take the form of a card. It can be a simple single-sided or double-sided card. It can also have a fold.</p>

<p>The card will be delivered in an envelope, which you donâ€™t need to worry about.</p>

<p>This should be a minimal type-based design that uses hierarchy, limited colour for emphasis, and a refined typographic treatment.</p>

